data.description:
**Motivated seller offering to contribute $15,000 toward interest rate buy down, closing costs, with full asking price!** This brick home is nestled just outside the gates of Hurlburt Field, offers the perfect blend of space, privacy, and convenience. This property has a range of features that make it a standout choice in today's market. 3% interest rate assumable VA mortgage for qualified buyers! As you enter the home, an archway leads you from the foyer to the dinging room and living room. The layout features two distinct wings, ensuring comfort and privacy for all residents. On one side, the hallway from the front door leads to two guest bedrooms and a bathroom complete with a single vanity and a shower/tub combo. Across the main living area, the other wing offers two additional guest rooms, an extra guest bathroom, and comfortable owner's quarters featuring an ensuite bathroom for added convenience. The u-shaped kitchen features recently replaced stainless steel appliances and an abundance of cabinet space, making meal preparation and storage a breeze. The indoor laundry area is conveniently located just off the kitchen, adding to the home's functionality. A standout feature of this home is the provision of two water heaters on opposite sides, ensuring that hot water is readily available without any hassle, even when multiple family members return from a day at the beach. In the rear of the home, you'll appreciate the large screened in porch and privacy fence encircling the backyard, providing a peaceful oasis for outdoor activities, relaxation, and entertaining. 

Find peace of mind for years to come with the long list of upgrades and features including roof replaced in 2021, HVAC and smart thermostat replaced in 2022, New appliances in 2022, wood look tile and carpet installed and patio screens replaced in 2022, 1 water heater replaced in 2020, partial fence installed in 2020. Kitchen refrigerator, plus garage refrigerator and washer/dryer convey! 

For the astute investor, the high military turnover in the area makes this property an excellent rental opportunity. Its proximity to Hurlburt Field, Eglin Air Force Base, downtown Ft. Walton Beach, Destin and the pristine white-sand beaches of Navarre ensures a convenient and desirable location for potential tenants.
In this rapidly growing area, you'll find yourself just a short drive from essential amenities such as gas stations, grocery stores, ample dining options, and major retailers like Walmart, Kohl's, Lowe's, and more.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a spacious, versatile, and conveniently located property. Contact us today to schedule your private tour and make this house your new home! Note: The last 10 pictures on this listing are virtually staged to help visualize the space best use. Buyers to perform all due diligence and verify all pertinent facts.
